      "content": "Those thoughts sound incredibly heavy, but it's crucial to recognize that wanting freedom doesn't have to mean ending your life; you can still find moments of light without sacrificing your existence. Many people find relief not by letting go entirely, but by sharing your care with others so your family can reclaim their time and passions. Please consider speaking with a healthcare provider or counselor who can support you through this emotional turbulence without judgment.",
